descriptionNullable:
This dataset can be used to classify the following diseases:
1. Actinic keratosis
2. Atopic Dermatitis
3. Benign keratosis
4. Dermatofibroma
5. Melanocytic nevus
6. Melanoma
7. Squamous cell carcinoma
8. Tinea Ringworm Candidiasis
9. Vascular lesion
